    {
      "id": "1364a3fd-7793-49a3-9a4e-135905c3b94c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Students are one of the primary sources of data for educational contexts and it is in the benefit of theses institutions to use this data to identify students who may require special attention. The paper presents an hybrid of DT with SVM model for student performance. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1364a3fd-7793-49a3-9a4e-135905c3b94c",
        "parent": {
