    {
      "id": "00990f07-8f08-4fd6-a226-f95014f94b58",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Abstract does not explicitly mention the metrics used for evaluation but it does seem that DT was better (possible typo). Moreover, the authors have also identified 7 possible factors that affect student performance. ",
